{"tid":2129920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【疫情衝擊】全年恐虧逾25億　吉野家全球要關150家店","createTime":"2020-07-29T02:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T04:52:51.000Z","uid":73381,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ac34bcf430b20d789037f8c10f38d6b9debd4c3d","tid":2129920,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:45:52.000Z","msg":"吉野家在日本和國外約有3300家店，該公司計劃關閉的分店佔總數5%。另外，吉野家本年度原則上會凍結開設新店。<br />\n<br />\n吉野家社長河村泰貴在記者會上說：「新冠肺炎影響預料會持續很長一段時間。」河村泰貴表示，吉野家會削減成本並改良外帶產品，藉此讓該公司即使營收下滑也能獲利。<br />\n<br />\n吉野家5月底止年度第1季營收為396.81億日圓，比去年同期減少24.8%。吉野家年度第1季淨損40.87億日圓，不如去年同期的獲利10.97億日圓。吉野家本年度營收估為1723億日圓，比上年度減少20.3%，淨損估為90億日圓（約25.4億元台幣）。（林文彬／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20200729/MYWHL72HTROJABVSXXZ2BE2ZEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20200729%2FMYWHL72HTROJABVSXXZ2BE2ZEQ%2F&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=fcf30f3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20200729%2FMYWHL72HTROJABVSXXZ2BE2ZEQ%2F&h=9dea6707\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20200729/MYWHL72HTROJABVSXXZ2BE2ZEQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f5c897c1e5e5ec32c3e0e3fae9e54de207eb905c","tid":2129920,"uid":17907,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"幾時收返香港個經營權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda354f71dc92942493105ae3b934776d869c986","tid":2129920,"uid":101945,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"中國&amp;香港經營權俾了紅資一樣垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9dac397ede904a9d1fbf2bf96b9e65b02a6933","tid":2129920,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:57:14.000Z","msg":"咁少?"},{"pid":"9a176f8c36977b317d47239390bed95145de7bfe","tid":2129920,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re